{"parentUuid":"4ccb9846-9c6e-4ad3-8a1e-c3d72ebf6a56","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a5b760f7bd0b5bba3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01H94mYrxXra7u7UUdgjDUD4","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Claude 4 GPT-5 Gemini 2.5 capabilities 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Claude vs ChatGPT vs Copilot vs Gemini: 2026 Enterprise Guide | IntuitionLabs\",\"url\":\"https://intuitionlabs.ai/articles/claude-vs-chatgpt-vs-copilot-vs-gemini-enterprise-comparison\"},{\"title\":\"AI Comparisons 2026: ChatGPT vs Gemini vs Claude vs DeepSeek\",\"url\":\"https://gurusup.com/blog/ai-comparisons\"},{\"title\":\"Best AI Models 2026: Gemini, GPT, Claude for Projects - VERTU® Official Site\",\"url\":\"https://vertu.com/guides/best-ai-models-2026-gemini-gpt-claude-for-projects/\"},{\"title\":\"AI Updates Today (March 2026) – Latest AI Model Releases\",\"url\":\"https://llm-stats.com/llm-updates\"},{\"title\":\"AI Guide 2026: GPT-5.2, Claude 4.5, Gemini 3 & Llama 4 Compared\",\"url\":\"https://www.adwaitx.com/ai-implementation-guide-2026-models-tools/\"},{\"title\":\"Claude 4.5 vs. GPT-5.2 vs. Gemini 3: Best AI for Coding 2026 | VERTU\",\"url\":\"https://vertu.com/lifestyle/models-in-2026-the-ultimate-showdown-of-claude-4-5-gemini-3-and-chatgpt-5-2/\"},{\"title\":\"ChatGPT vs Gemini vs Claude Full 2026 Comparison: Complete Analysis, Features, Pricing, Workflow Impact, and Performance\",\"url\":\"https://www.datastudios.org/post/chatgpt-vs-gemini-vs-claude-full-2026-comparison-complete-analysis-features-pricing-workflow-imp\"},{\"title\":\"Gpt-5.1 vs Gemini 3 Pro vs Claude Opus 4.5 Breakdown Report\",\"url\":\"https://www.vellum.ai/blog/flagship-model-report\"},{\"title\":\"ChatGPT vs Claude vs Gemini 2026: Coding Benchmarks, Essay Writing & Full Comparison\",\"url\":\"https://freeacademy.ai/blog/chatgpt-vs-claude-vs-gemini-comparison-2026\"},{\"title\":\"AI Guide for 2026: GPT-5.2 vs. Gemini 3 Pro vs. Claude 4.5 — Which Model When? |Skymod\",\"url\":\"https://skymod.tech/ai-guide-for-2026-gpt-5-2-vs-gemini-3-pro-vs-claude-4-5-which-model-when/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about Claude 4, GPT-5, Gemini 2.5, and their capabilities in 2026:\n\n## Current State of Major AI Models (2026)\n\nAs of 2026, OpenAI's ChatGPT, Anthropic's Claude, Microsoft's Copilot, and Google's Gemini are the leading generative AI solutions targeting businesses.\n\n### Key Model Versions and Capabilities\n\n**Claude:** Claude Opus 4.6 achieves record scores on coding tests, surpassing Google Gemini 3 Pro. Claude achieves 80.9% on SWE-bench Verified compared to GPT-5.2's ~70% and Gemini's ~65%.\n\n**GPT-5.x:** ChatGPT (GPT-5.2) is rated highly on general IQ-like tests (e.g. LSAT, BarExam, MedQA) often outperforming Gemini.\n\n**Gemini 3:** Gemini 3.1 Pro, the current flagship, is described as an \"AI Supercomputer in a model\" -- aiming to combine large context (O(1,000) pages), multimodality, and advanced reasoning seamlessly.\n\n### Specialized Strengths\n\nClaude Opus 4.5 currently leads on SWE-Bench and Terminal-bench, making it a strong choice for engineering-heavy workflows. Gemini 3 Pro is currently the strongest in multimodal reasoning and the only model with reported Video-MMMU results, making it a better fit for agents that need to \"see,\" analyze, or process real-world data.\n\nNote: The search results reference Gemini 3 and Gemini 3.1 Pro as current models; I did not find specific information about \"Gemini 2.5\" in these 2026 comparisons.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"0519e3b7-3405-4ae6-b404-f1d28a18d035","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:18:55.710Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"4ccb9846-9c6e-4ad3-8a1e-c3d72ebf6a56","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
