{"parentUuid":"0b209277-71e1-4c96-ac6c-30f626262e5e","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a5b760f7bd0b5bba3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01PonRynCA5MqFGG2itrrm16","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"NVIDIA compute GPU access inequality AI 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Nvidia's GTC will mark an AI chip pivot. Here's why the CPU is taking center stage\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/13/nvidia-gtc-ai-jensen-huang-cpu-gpu.html\"},{\"title\":\"AI Conference | Mar 16-19, 2026 San Jose | NVIDIA GTC\",\"url\":\"https://www.nvidia.com/gtc/\"},{\"title\":\"The AI Boom Is Running Into Physical Limits | InvestorPlace\",\"url\":\"https://investorplace.com/hypergrowthinvesting/2026/03/the-ai-boom-is-running-into-physical-limits/\"},{\"title\":\"Top 12 NVIDIA GPUs for AI Training & Inference in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.atlantic.net/gpu-server-hosting/top-nvidia-gpus-for-ai-training-and-inference/\"},{\"title\":\"Top NVIDIA GPUs for AI & ML in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.hostingseekers.com/blog/best-nvidia-gpus-for-ai-and-machine-learning/\"},{\"title\":\"NVIDIA Accelerates AI for Over 80 New Science Systems Worldwide | NVIDIA Blog\",\"url\":\"https://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/sc25-new-science-systems-worldwide/\"},{\"title\":\"The GPU Capacity Crisis: Why Enterprises Are Rethinking ...\",\"url\":\"https://vexxhost.com/blog/gpu-capacity-crisis-ai-infrastructure-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"12 best GPUs for AI and machine learning in 2026 | Blog — Northflank\",\"url\":\"https://northflank.com/blog/best-gpu-for-ai\"},{\"title\":\"NVIDIA Corporation - NVIDIA Kicks Off the Next Generation of AI With Rubin — Six New Chips, One Incredible AI Supercomputer\",\"url\":\"https://investor.nvidia.com/news/press-release-details/2026/NVIDIA-Kicks-Off-the-Next-Generation-of-AI-With-Rubin--Six-New-Chips-One-Incredible-AI-Supercomputer/default.aspx\"},{\"title\":\"Why Nvidia's AI Empire Faces a Reckoning in 2026 - EE Times\",\"url\":\"https://www.eetimes.com/why-nvidias-ai-empire-faces-a-reckoning-in-2026/\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found regarding NVIDIA compute GPU access inequality in AI as of 2026:\n\n## GPU Access Crisis and Inequality\n\nAI demand is outpacing GPU supply, with enterprises rethinking where AI workloads run in 2026. The shortage is severe: lead times for data-center GPUs now run from 36 to 52 weeks, and Chinese technology companies have placed orders for more than 2 million H200 chips for 2026, while Nvidia currently holds just 700,000 units in stock.\n\n## Memory Supply Bottlenecks\n\nThe current compute crunch is a product of explosive demand from AI workloads, limited supplies of high-bandwidth memory, and tight advanced packaging capacity. Memory suppliers have shifted capacity away from DDR and GDDR to HBM, with analysts noting that data centers will consume the majority of global memory supply in 2026.\n\n## Shifting Infrastructure Patterns\n\nThe scarcity is reshaping how organizations deploy AI: A 2024 CIO survey from Barclays revealed that 83% of enterprises are planning to move workloads from public cloud to private or on-premises solutions, up from just 43% in 2021. Organizations are keeping burst and experimentation workloads in public cloud while repatriating predictable, high-utilization AI workloads to controlled infrastructure, with cloud-smart being the 2026 reality of running workloads where the economics make sense.\n\n## Pricing Pressures\n\nOn January 4, 2026, AWS updated its EC2 Capacity Blocks pricing page, with the p5e.48xlarge instance jumping from $34.61 to $39.80 per hour across most regions.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"cbde9f44-8153-426c-b05d-491796c65afc","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:19:26.297Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"0b209277-71e1-4c96-ac6c-30f626262e5e","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
