{"parentUuid":"27544576-8f63-4f99-b774-c25515f6bbdb","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a5b760f7bd0b5bba3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Tyfhgtq417GKAxBsefAKw5","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"AI education students teachers impact 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Designing the 2026 Classroom: Emerging Learning Trends in an AI-Powered Education System - Faculty Focus | Higher Ed Teaching & Learning\",\"url\":\"https://www.facultyfocus.com/articles/teaching-with-technology-articles/designing-the-2026-classroom-emerging-learning-trends-in-an-ai-powered-education-system/\"},{\"title\":\"Some predictions about AI in education in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://fordhaminstitute.org/national/commentary/some-predictions-about-ai-education-2026\"},{\"title\":\"OECD Digital Education Outlook 2026 | OECD\",\"url\":\"https://www.oecd.org/en/publications/oecd-digital-education-outlook-2026_062a7394-en.html\"},{\"title\":\"25 AI in Education Statistics to Guide Your Learning Strategy in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.engageli.com/blog/ai-in-education-statistics\"},{\"title\":\"49 predictions about edtech, innovation, and--yes--AI in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.eschoolnews.com/innovative-teaching/2026/01/01/draft-2026-predictions/\"},{\"title\":\"The Latest AI in Education Statistics (2026) - Programs.com\",\"url\":\"https://programs.com/resources/ai-education-statistics/\"},{\"title\":\"AI’s future for students is in our hands | Brookings\",\"url\":\"https://www.brookings.edu/articles/ais-future-for-students-is-in-our-hands/\"},{\"title\":\"75 AI in Education Statistics 2026 (Global Trends & Facts)\",\"url\":\"https://www.demandsage.com/ai-in-education-statistics/\"},{\"title\":\"AI Trends in Education 2026: What’s Changing | TeachBetter.ai\",\"url\":\"https://teachbetter.ai/ai-trends-in-education-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"AI in education: What's really happening in US schools in 2026\",\"url\":\"https://thirdspacelearning.com/us/blog/ai-in-education/\"}]\n\nI've found comprehensive information about AI's impact on education, students, and teachers in 2026. Here are the key findings:\n\n## Current AI Adoption\n\nStudent use of AI for school-related purposes jumped 26% since last school year, while educator use rose 21% over the same period. Global student AI usage jumped from 66% in 2024 to 92% in 2025, and by the start of 2026, it is estimated that 86% of all students in higher education utilize AI as their primary research and brainstorming partner.\n\n## Impact on Students\n\nAI's impact extends across primary, secondary, and higher education, supporting personalized learning that adapts to individual needs, delivers instant feedback, enhances student engagement and outcomes, and reduces administrative demands on teachers. A 2025 Harvard University physics study found that students using AI tutors learned more than twice as much in less time compared to those in traditional active-learning classrooms.\n\n## Impact on Teachers\n\nTeachers who use AI tools at least weekly save an average of 5.9 hours per week, which adds up to roughly 6 extra weeks of reclaimed time across a standard school year. 69% of teachers said AI tools have improved their teaching methods, while 55% agreed that it has given them more time to interact directly with students.\n\n## Concerns and Challenges\n\n70% of teachers worry that AI weakens critical thinking and research skills, and over half of the students agree that using AI in class makes them feel less connected to their teachers. Additionally, although most teachers and students use AI, under half have received no training or guidance from their institutions.\n\n## Future Outlook for 2026\n\nIn 2026, learning how to use these learning tools will be crucial, and experts have said that the best way for schools to manage AI risks is through teacher training and student literacy lessons.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"7ed621f2-76b8-408f-bfb4-9207111f38fe","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:19:48.913Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"27544576-8f63-4f99-b774-c25515f6bbdb","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
