{"parentUuid":"fb2e3a78-c8b2-4b5a-a9a4-1aae90be89cb","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a5b760f7bd0b5bba3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01LH3sxRovDtz7Lwd13Tnxdw","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"AI funding investment 2026 where money flowing venture capital\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Crunchbase Predicts: Why Top VCs Expect More Venture Dollars, Bigger Rounds And Fewer Winners In 2026\",\"url\":\"https://news.crunchbase.com/venture/crunchbase-predicts-vcs-expect-more-funding-ai-ipo-ma-2026-forecast/\"},{\"title\":\"Here are the 17 US-based AI companies that have raised $100M or more in 2026 | TechCrunch\",\"url\":\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/02/17/here-are-the-17-us-based-ai-companies-that-have-raised-100m-or-more-in-2026/\"},{\"title\":\"AI Startup Funding Trends 2026: Data, Rounds & What's Next\",\"url\":\"https://qubit.capital/blog/ai-startup-fundraising-trends\"},{\"title\":\"AI Still Dominates as Media VC Deals Fell 69% to $165 Million in First 2 Months of 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.thewrap.com/industry-news/deals-ma/the-funding-file-venture-capital-investment-january-february-2026-update/\"},{\"title\":\"AI supercharged 2025's biggest deals – both directly and indirectly - Global Venturing\",\"url\":\"https://globalventuring.com/corporate/energy-and-natural-resources/ai-supercharges-2025-biggest-deals/\"},{\"title\":\"6 Charts That Show The Big AI Funding Trends Of 2025\",\"url\":\"https://news.crunchbase.com/ai/big-funding-trends-charts-eoy-2025/\"},{\"title\":\"AI Funding Tracker | AI Startup Investment Roundups 2026\",\"url\":\"https://aifundingtracker.com/\"},{\"title\":\"85 Hottest AI Startups to Watch in 2026 [By Valuation, Funding, & Growth]\",\"url\":\"https://wellows.com/blog/ai-startups/\"},{\"title\":\"AI Startup Funding News Today – Latest Deals & Rounds 2026\",\"url\":\"https://aifundingtracker.com/ai-startup-funding-news-today/\"},{\"title\":\"In 2026, venture capital’s hunger for AI will be insatiable - Fast Company\",\"url\":\"https://www.fastcompany.com/91465347/2026-venture-capital-artificial-intelligence-openai-anduril\"}]\n\nBased on the web search results, here's what I found about AI funding and venture capital flows in 2026:\n\n## Overall Capital Deployment\n\nGlobal venture capital deployment is expected to increase from the low $400 billion to the high $400 billion mark, which implies a 10% increase in dollars deployed.\n\n## Where Money is Flowing\n\n**Foundation Models and Large AI Companies Dominating:**\nOpenAI closed the largest private funding round in history — $110B at a $730B pre-money valuation, led by Amazon ($50B), Nvidia ($30B), and SoftBank ($30B). Anthropic closed a landmark $30 billion Series G at $380 billion post-money — the second-largest private venture deal in history.\n\n**AI Infrastructure and Physical AI:**\nAI infrastructure (cost/performance breakthroughs), defense (geopolitical), healthcare AI (provider margin pressure) will gain share, while consumer and horizontal SaaS will lose. Physical AI arrived as a co-equal investment theme: Waymo ($16B), Wayve ($1.2B), Waabi ($1B), Bedrock Robotics ($270M), Skyryse ($300M), and Einride collectively raised over $19B for autonomous systems in a single month.\n\n**Capital Concentration:**\nAI startups attracted about 131.5 billion dollars in venture funding, growing roughly 52 percent while funding to non AI startups slipped almost 10 percent to around 237 billion dollars. The two largest foundation companies, OpenAI and Anthropic, alone captured 14% of global venture investment this year.\n\n**Shift from AI \"Wrappers\":**\nThe shift from \"AI wrappers\" to infrastructure has already happened. Last year demonstrated that it's difficult to survive as an AI wrapper company.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"d3d9f61d-6ed4-4ed8-847b-b0188bed94cf","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:19:51.039Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"fb2e3a78-c8b2-4b5a-a9a4-1aae90be89cb","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
