{"parentUuid":"39bed986-da67-4e67-beac-97fa3ee05c3b","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"a5b760f7bd0b5bba3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019FcQsrXRzk6CD4AdV6Ro27","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Anthropic electricity pledge carbon offset AI environmental impact 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Why is Anthropic Pledging to Offset its AI Energy Costs? | Sustainability Magazine\",\"url\":\"https://sustainabilitymag.com/news/why-anthropic-pledging-offset-ai-energy-costs\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic Pledges 100% Grid Upgrade Funding to Offset AI Data Center Power Costs: 2026 Impact Analysis | AI News Detail\",\"url\":\"https://blockchain.news/ainews/anthropic-pledges-100-grid-upgrade-funding-to-offset-ai-data-center-power-costs-2026-impact-analysis\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic vows to protect consumers from rising electricity costs - SiliconANGLE\",\"url\":\"https://siliconangle.com/2026/02/11/anthropic-vows-protect-consumers-rising-electricity-costs/\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic\",\"url\":\"https://www.anthropic.com/news/investing-in-energy-to-secure-america-s-ai-future\"},{\"title\":\"Why Anthropic is Offsetting Grid Impacts of its Data Centres | AI Magazine\",\"url\":\"https://aimagazine.com/news/why-anthropic-is-offsetting-grid-impacts-of-its-data-centres\"},{\"title\":\"The AI Energy Reckoning: How is Anthropic Securing Grids? | Energy Magazine\",\"url\":\"https://energydigital.com/news/the-ai-energy-reckoning-how-is-anthropic-securing-grids\"},{\"title\":\"Your AI Carbon Footprint: What Every Query Really Costs - Earth911\",\"url\":\"https://earth911.com/business-policy/your-ai-carbon-footprint-what-every-query-really-costs/\"},{\"title\":\"White House Tech Power funding push challenges ratepayer costs - AI CERTs News\",\"url\":\"https://www.aicerts.ai/news/white-house-tech-power-funding-push-challenges-ratepayer-costs/\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic Pledge: Paying for AI Data Centre Power Costs\",\"url\":\"https://www.aryahamrah.com/en/anthropic-pledge-ai-data-centre-power-costs-en/\"},{\"title\":\"Anthropic Emissions Breakdown & Climate Score | DitchCarbon\",\"url\":\"https://ditchcarbon.com/organizations/anthropic\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about Anthropic's electricity pledge, carbon offset efforts, and environmental impact in 2026:\n\n## Anthropic's Electricity Pledge (2026)\n\nAnthropic announced on February 11, 2026, that they will cover 100 percent of electricity price increases from their data centers, pay for all grid upgrades, and invest in new power and strain-reduction systems to protect ratepayers.\n\n## Key Commitments\n\nThe pledge includes several major components:\n\n1. **Grid Upgrade Costs**: Anthropic will pay for 100% of the grid upgrades needed to interconnect their data centers, paid through increases to their monthly electricity charges, including the shares of these costs that would otherwise be passed onto consumers.\n\n2. **Price Offset**: In regions where additional generation isn't yet available, the company pledges to collaborate with utilities and independent experts to assess and offset any price increases driven by its own energy consumption.\n\n3. **Operational Efficiency**: The company is investing in curtailment systems that cut their data centers' power usage during periods of peak demand, as well as grid optimization tools, both of which help keep prices lower for ratepayers.\n\n## Environmental Measures\n\nThe company has emphasized its commitment to being a responsible neighbor, addressing environmental impacts through measures such as water-efficient cooling systems. Additionally, Anthropic believes that AI will be a powerful tool to support emissions reductions, advance clean energy innovation, and streamline efficiencies.\n\n## Carbon Emissions Disclosure Gap\n\nHowever, as of March 2026, Anthropic has not reported Scope 1, 2, or 3 emissions in any public filing.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"a02222b0-b6e3-4efa-a4de-ed00da6ae03d","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:20:14.614Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"39bed986-da67-4e67-beac-97fa3ee05c3b","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
